window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>My husband hates me. But he’s also the only man who can save me.</p> <p>Taken by a stranger, Santiago is my only hope. Except that I don’t know if he’s dead or alive. And for as cruel as he can be, the thought he might be gone is unbearable. </p> <p>But he has nine lives, my monster. </p> <p>He’s not finished with me yet. And soon I’m back at The Manor. Locked in my room. At his mercy. </p> <p>I know I am despised. I know I have become the face of his vengeance. </p> <p>But there’s something else, too. Something between us. It’s a dark and gnarled thing. And it has its claws around my heart.</p>"; 
